Content.bodyText:
Hi there, 

This is a message for sunsetlinger, sorry to hear that you couldn't get through to someone that could understand. We would be delighted to take the order for your son's wedding. Please call 07979478529 to discuss your needs. The Saigon Lounge is also a few minutes from the amazing Wandsworth registry office. We also take bookings for weddings.

Look forward to hearing from you.

Sam

Saigon Lounge
